T02D3655:263b-1: a'arya ya m'anta ka s'a dha nam /
T02D3655:263b-3: 'phags pa gshin rje gshed kyi sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02D3655:263b-4: 'phags pa khro bo gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3655:263b-5: de bzhin du aom h'um zhes bya ba'i sa bon las bskyed la /
T02D3655:263b-6: khro bo'i skyil krung gis nyi ma la gnas pa'i
T02D3655:263b-7: yi ge h'um las byung ba'i gshin rje gshed rab
T02D3655:263b-8: tu khros pa / zhal drug pa phyag drug pa /
T02D3655:263b-9: dbu skra gyen du brdzes pa /
T02D3655:263b-10: ma he la chibs pa g-yon brkyang bas bzhugs pa /
T02D3655:263b-11: mi'i thod pa dang rgyu mas brgyan pa /
T02D3655:263b-12: shin tu 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can /
T02D3655:263b-13: stag gi pags pa'i smad g-yogs can /
T02D3655:263b-14: phyag g-yas na ral gri dang rdo rje bsnams pa /
T02D3655:263b-16: rdo rje gtun shing bsnams pa /
T02D3655:263b-17: cod pan mi bskyod pas mtshan pa bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3655:263b-18: de nas dam tshig gi phyag rgya bcing bar bya ste /
T02D3655:263b-19: thal mo khong stong du sbyar la mthe bong gnyis
T02D3655:263b-20: dang mdzub mo gnyis so sor phye la gung mo
T02D3655:263b-21: gnyis kyi tshigs gsum pa bcag par bya'o //
T02D3655:264a-1: t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
